    "closed_at": "2026-03-29T22:49:24Z",
    "comment_data": [],
    "comment_regular_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Tests seem to pass. Just had to update unit tests with the new `close_buffer()` signature, fix a small bug in the port of v9.1.0678, and reset `b_nwindows` in `free_all_mem()` (which also seems to have fixed all the existing `X lua references were leaked!` warnings on the CI?)\r\n\r\nPretty cool. I'll still probably spend more time combing over stuff because I'm paranoid. :grin: ",
