            "body": "Some remarks in the commit messages.\r\n\r\nI think it's safest to wait until after the release with these fixes, in case I screwed something up. (But I think it's solid :pray:; I'll add `revisit-at-release` as an advisory label anyway)\r\n\r\nAlso, maybe 9.2.0252 should be considered a partial patch? I 'unno.",
